ygData.messageBody:
I dunno if they are in (maybe random drops in Sky like some of the caster
spells? *shrug*), but I would like to know if anyone has found any of them.
Like many of you I will most likely be hitting 51 shortly after logging in
on Monday, and I WANT Song 51 ASAP! =) If the song truly is a 75% speed
increase + levitate + invis + see invis, well as far as Kunark and it's huge
zones are concerned, it will be the best thing since Wonderbread. If anyone
gets info on where and how to obtain our new songs please post here as soon
as possible.

Oh yeh, killed Maestro tonight, only had Mempo. Not complaining tho - our
monk needs it for when he is spotting on hamburger hill at the Fear portal
(damn blind monkeys). =)

Sartori Stormraven<Legion>
50th Bard of Veeshan, humble servant of Quellious
